<BaseLayout title="Research" description="My research explores how different forms of polarisation relate to democratic health.">

  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 240px; gap: 2rem; align-items: start;">
        <div>
          <h1>Research</h1>
          <p class="intro" style="text-align: justify;">What drives my research is a deceptively simple question: <strong>when does conflict become a threat to democracy?</strong> Our societies are polarising, and the most common reaction is to see that as inherently dangerous. My work, instead, is built on the conviction that understanding this distinction — between the conflict that democracies need and the conflict that destroys them — is one of the most urgent tasks for political science today. In doing so, I have developed a strong interest in studying different sorts of polarisation, and the broader socio-institutional framework within which it erupts.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; padding-top: 3.5rem;">
          <a href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=7Pmo70UAAAAJ&hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; text-align: center; font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); transition: border-color 0.15s ease;">
            <span style="display: block; font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 0.125rem;">Google Scholar</span>
            Full publication metrics
          </a>
          <a href="https://researchportal.vub.be/en/persons/kamil-bernaerts" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1rem; border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; text-align: center; font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary); transition: border-color 0.15s ease;">
            <span style="display: block; font-weight: 500; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 0.125rem;">VUB Research Portal</span>
            Institutional profile
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

